<plot>Widowed Manorama lives a wealthy lifestyle in India. She has her niece visit her and makes her the sole heir to her estate. The household peace and serenity will soon be shattered by the appearance of Jagjit and a butler - who are not who they claim to be; an attractive woman named Munni; a friendly young man named Munna, and a disfigured tall and seemingly invincible man - who may be one of the Undead. Things get even more complicated when Manorama decides to change her will and starts acting completely out of character.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?067963</url></doc>
